wear
Discworld player help
wear

.SH Name
.SI 5
wear - Wear items of clothing and armour
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
wear <item>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Wear is how you don your armour.  You type wear followed by the items you wish
to wear.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> wear shield
> wear second shield
> wear all
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
remove
.EI
